Uses of Package
Main.Scores

Packages that use Main.Scores
Package Description
Main.Others
This package holds the other java classes which cannot be clearly fitted into another package.
Main.Scores
This package holds the java classes which control and display the ranking of the player.
  • Classes in Main.Scores used by Main.Others
    Class Description
    Highscore
    Public class Highscore is responsible for generating and showing the top 10 highest scores for each level and the total highscore for the game on the Highscore Board which can be reached from the HomeMenu.
  • Classes in Main.Scores used by Main.Scores
    Class Description
    Score
    Class Score is used as a linked list to load and hold the basic information about the player such as ranking, name, level type, time and score after completing a level.
